a football World Cup\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 763}, {\"ngram\": \"that featured air-conditioned stadiums\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 819}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 821, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"a more sober model\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"global sports events\", \"from\": 882, \"to\": 902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope Paris 2024's efforts to reduce its impacts can demonstrate that it is possible to do things differently,\\\" Ms Georgina Grenon, director of environmental excellence for the organising committee, told AFP in a recent interview.\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 913, \"end\": 923, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1296065154577784e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999977126208, \"rank\": 2.2873403430176173e-09, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its impacts\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1004}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Georgina Grenon\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1047}, {\"ngram\": \"environmental excellence\", \"from\": 1051, \"to\": 1075}, {\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"a recent interview\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the main differences will be in the overall carbon emissions, with organisers aiming for half of the amount generated by the 2012 Olympics in London and the 2016 edition in Rio de Janeiro.\", \"from\": 1139, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1288, \"end\": 1294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.99999992928588, \"rank\": 6.805001939701386e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7459110151451533e-17, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main differences\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1166}, {\"ngram\": \"the overall carbon emissions\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1206}, {\"ngram\": \"organisers\", \"from\": 1213, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"the amount\", \"from\": 1243, \"to\": 1253}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2012 Olympics\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2016 edition\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 initially set a target equivalent to 1.58 million tonnes of carbon dioxide, but that ambition has been lowered to around 1.75 million tonnes.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1336, \"end\": 1346, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1296065154577784e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a target\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1369}, {\"ngram\": \"1.58 million tonnes\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"carbon dioxide\", \"from\": 1407, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"that ambition\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1440}, {\"ngram\": \"around 1.75 million tonnes\", \"from\": 1461, \"to\": 1487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Something we are uncertain of today is the (carbon impact of) spectators,\\\" said Ms Grenon when asked if the latest target can be met.\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1624, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Something\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1500}, {\"ngram\": \"today\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"the (carbon impact\", \"from\": 1530, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"spectators\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1563}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Grenon\", \"from\": 1571, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"the latest target\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1612}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the key factors will be the number of heavily polluting plane journeys linked to the Gamesand \\\"we have not yet sold all the tickets\\\", she added.\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the key factors\", \"from\": 1633, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1667}, {\"ngram\": \"heavily polluting plane journeys\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gamesand\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"all the tickets\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An external consulting firm will be tasked with auditing the impact of travel, construction, catering and sports equipment, with final figures set to be published in October.\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1953, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"An external consulting firm\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1806}, {\"ngram\": \"the impact\", \"from\": 1836, \"to\": 1846}, {\"ngram\": \"travel\", \"from\": 1850, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"construction\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1870}, {\"ngram\": \"catering\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 1901}, {\"ngram\": \"final figures\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1921}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The key to reducing Paris' carbon footprint was contained in the city's original bid.\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 2040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1975, \"end\": 1980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.988028362711494e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The key\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"the city's original bid\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2039}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organisers promised to use either existing or temporary venues for 95 per cent of the sports events, meaning they could avoid building new stadiums from scratch.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organisers\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2052}, {\"ngram\": \"either existing or temporary venues\", \"from\": 2069, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"95 per cent\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2120}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports events\", \"from\": 2124, \"to\": 2141}, {\"ngram\": \"new stadiums\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"scratch\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2202}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only major new-build projects have been an aquatics centre, a mid-sized venue in Paris for badminton and gymnastics, and the athletes' village in the deprived Paris suburb of Seine-Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2290, \"end\": 2295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.988028362711494e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2368, \"end\": 2373, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.988028362711494e-16, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only major new-build projects\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2238}, {\"ngram\": \"an aquatics centre\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"a mid-sized venue\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2286}, {\"ngram\": \"badminton\", \"from\": 2300, \"to\": 2309}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 2314, \"to\": 2324}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 2330, \"to\": 2351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Contractors for the village had to agree to reduce emissions resulting from their buildings by 30 per cent compared with standard construction, meaning many of them experimented with low-carbon concrete and wood.\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2616, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Contractors\", \"from\": 2404, \"to\": 2415}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 2420, \"to\": 2431}, {\"ngram\": \"emissions\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"their buildings\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"30 per cent\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2510}, {\"ngram\": \"standard construction\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2546}, {\"ngram\": \"low-carbon concrete\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2606}, {\"ngram\": \"wood\", \"from\": 2611, \"to\": 2615}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Other changes included connecting up all the sports venues to the electricity mains supply, meaning stadium operators do not rely on diesel generators for power.\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2779, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Other changes\", \"from\": 2618, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"all the sports venues\", \"from\": 2655, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"the electricity mains supply\", \"from\": 2680, \"to\": 2708}, {\"ngram\": \"stadium operators\", \"from\": 2718, \"to\": 2735}, {\"ngram\": \"diesel generators\", \"from\": 2751, \"to\": 2768}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 2773, \"to\": 2778}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To give you an idea of the volume of diesel for the London Games, there were 4 million litres burned just for electricity purposes,\\\" said Ms Grenon.\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2930, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an idea\", \"from\": 2794, \"to\": 2801}, {\"ngram\": \"the volume\", \"from\": 2805, \"to\": 2815}, {\"ngram\": \"diesel\", \"from\": 2819, \"to\": 2825}, {\"ngram\": \"the London Games\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"4 million litres\", \"from\": 2859, \"to\": 2875}, {\"ngram\": \"electricity purposes\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"Ms Grenon\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Coca-Cola - a top Olympics sponsor - has agreed to install 700 newly designed drink fountains at Olympic venues, meaning that around 50 per cent of soft drinks will be served without a plastic bottle.\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 3132, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Coca-Cola\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"a top Olympics sponsor\", \"from\": 2944, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"700 newly designed drink fountains\", \"from\": 2991, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic venues\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"around 50 per cent\", \"from\": 3058, \"to\": 3076}, {\"ngram\": \"soft drinks\", \"from\": 3080, \"to\": 3091}, {\"ngram\": \"a plastic bottle\", \"from\": 3115, \"to\": 3131}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Additionally, meals at sports venues will be 60 per cent vegetarian.\", \"from\": 3134, \"to\": 3202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"meals\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3153}, {\"ngram\": \"sports venues\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3170}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 3186, \"to\": 3190}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recycling and reuse clauses were routinely written into equipment supplier contracts.\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3288, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Recycling and reuse clauses\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3230}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment supplier contracts\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3287}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All of the energy supplied to the Games by national energy group EDF will be from renewable sources.\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3389, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 3296, \"to\": 3306}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3319, \"to\": 3328}, {\"ngram\": \"national energy group\", \"from\": 3332, \"to\": 3353}, {\"ngram\": \"EDF\", \"from\": 3354, \"to\": 3357}, {\"ngram\": \"renewable sources\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3388}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where Games organisers still face an uphill battle to convince observers is their policy on compensating for their emissions - something known as \\\"carbon offsetting\\\".\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Games organisers\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"an uphill battle\", \"from\": 3425, \"to\": 3441}, {\"ngram\": \"observers\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"their policy\", \"from\": 3467, \"to\": 3479}, {\"ngram\": \"their emissions\", \"from\": 3500, \"to\": 3515}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3518, \"to\": 3527}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even if they meet their emissions target of 1.75 million tonnes, it would be the equivalent of the annual carbon footprint of a French town of 200,000 people.\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3717, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3687, \"end\": 3698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenchtown_(ghost_town),_Maryland\", \"score\": 0.999967104937146, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French town\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenchtown_(ghost_town),_Maryland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Frenchtown_(ghost_town),_Maryland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their emissions target\", \"from\": 3577, \"to\": 3599}, {\"ngram\": \"1.75 million tonnes\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3622}, {\"ngram\": \"the equivalent\", \"from\": 3636, \"to\": 3650}, {\"ngram\": \"the annual carbon footprint\", \"from\": 3654, \"to\": 3681}, {\"ngram\": \"200,000 people\", \"from\": 3702, \"to\": 3716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They initially claimed that Paris 2024 would be \\\"carbon-positive\\\", meaning that the organising committee would invest in projects such as tree-planting that would capture more carbon dioxide over their lifetimes than the Games would emit.\", \"from\": 3719, \"to\": 3957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3747, \"end\": 3757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.1296065154577784e-17, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the organising committee\", \"from\": 3799, \"to\": 3823}, {\"ngram\": \"projects\", \"from\": 3840, \"to\": 3848}, {\"ngram\": \"tree-planting\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 3870}, {\"ngram\": \"more carbon dioxide\", \"from\": 3890, \"to\": 3909}, {\"ngram\": \"their lifetimes\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3930}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This target has also been revised downwards - the Games now aim to be \\\"carbon-neutral\\\" - and a tender for an offsetting project in France was cancelled in late2023for budget reasons, Ms Grenon said.\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 4157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4090, \"end\": 4096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9994121683993358, \"rank\": 0.000533196424873429, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc